		>"BRIEFING_POINT_TABLE" - Briefing, sometime point table
		>"TALKING" - Standing, hands move
		>"KNEEL" - Kneeling, with rifle
		>"KNEEL_U" - Kneeling
		>"EXERCICE" - Pushup and squat

		>"WARMUP" - Warm up, with rifle
		>"WARMUP_KNEEL" - Warm up, kneeling, with rifle
